OL,3,CWill Rachel Reeves' tax smorgasbord
OL,4,Cmake it out the kitchen?
OL,6,FHere are my estimates of the negative
OL,7,For loss side of the profit and loss
OL,8,Faccount Chancellor Rachel Reeves will
OL,9,Freveal in Wednesday's Budget tomorrow,
OL,10,Fas audited (as it were) by the Office
OL,11,Ffor Budget Responsibility (as per the
OL,12,Fsurreal accounting of fiscal rules
OL,13,Fbalances five years hence).
OL,15,FWe start with the March 2025 headroom
OL,16,Fof #9.9bn.
OL,18,FMinus #21bn from the OBR supply side
OL,19,Freview, which slashed productivity and
OL,20,Fgrowth forecasts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
