OL,3,CWill Rachel Reeves' tax smorgasbord
OL,4,Cmake it out the kitchen?
OL,6,FMinus #7bn from welfare and winter
OL,7,Ffuel u-turns.
OL,9,FMinus #3.6bn from ending the two-child
OL,10,Flimit on universal credit.
OL,12,FMinus #10bn (circa) to fatten headroom
OL,13,Fto around #20bn.
OL,15,FThis equals a cumulative hole of #40bn.
OL,17,FBut if we add back #10bn or so from
OL,18,FOBR's upgrade of future tax revenues
OL,19,Ffrom the existing tax base, this
OL,20,Fleaves #30bn to find from:
