OL,3,CWill Rachel Reeves' tax smorgasbord
OL,4,Cmake it out the kitchen?
OL,6,FMuch of the tax rises, including the
OL,7,Fpension, tax threshold and mansion
OL,8,Fchanges, are not expected to bite till
OL,9,F2028, and some of the nations'
OL,10,Fcreditors will interpret that delay as
OL,11,Ftoo close to a general election to be
OL,12,Fcredible.
OL,14,FAlso, investors always attach a
OL,15,Fmassive discount to promises that HMRC
OL,16,Fwill increase the tax take from
OL,17,Favoiders.
