OL,3,CWill Rachel Reeves' tax smorgasbord
OL,4,Cmake it out the kitchen?
OL,6,FFootnote: The bit I am missing is the
OL,7,Fcost of reducing our energy bills by
OL,8,Fmoving climate levies from the
OL,9,Fcustomer to the taxpayer.
OL,11,FOpinion: Assessing the credibility of
OL,12,Fthe budget may not be the work of an
OL,13,Finstant.
OL,15,FNutshell: so much of the tax
OL,16,Fsmorgasbord will be so back-dated that
OL,17,Fyou may wonder - if you are a UK
OL,18,Fgovernment creditor - whether it will
OL,19,Fever come out of the kitchen.
